headline: Arthur J. Gallagher acquires Wilkins & Associates Insurance Services
summary: Arthur J. Gallagher (AJG) & Co. announced the acquisition of Reno, Nevada-based Wilkins & Associates Insurance Services. Terms of the transaction were not disclosed. Wilkins & Associates, founded by Tom and Melanie Wilkins, is a retail insurance broker serving commercial and personal lines clients in Reno and western Nevada.
